{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"handler.preventExtensions()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/preventExtensions","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">Standard built-in objects</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy\"><code>Proxy/handler</code></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>メソッド</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/apply\"><code>handler.apply()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/construct\"><code>handler.construct()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/defineProperty\"><code>handler.defineProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/deleteProperty\"><code>handler.deleteProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/get\"><code>handler.get()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/getOwnPropertyDescriptor\"><code>handler.getOwnPropertyDescriptor()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/getPrototypeOf\"><code>handler.getPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/has\"><code>handler.has()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/isExtensible\"><code>handler.isExtensible()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/ownKeys\"><code>handler.ownKeys()</code></a></li><li><em><code>handler.preventExtensions()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/set\"><code>handler.set()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/setPrototypeOf\"><code>handler.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>handler.preventExtensions()</code></strong> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/preventExtensions\"><code>Object.preventExtensions()</code></a> に対するトラップです。</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"692\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/proxyhandler-preventextensions.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> p <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Proxy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">preventExtensions</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">target</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<p>次の引数は <code>preventExtensions()</code> メソッドに渡されます。 <code>this</code> はハンドラーにバインドされます。</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"target\"><code><var>target</var></code></dt>\n <dd>ターゲットオブジェクトです。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>preventExtensions()</code> メソッドは真偽値を返さなければなりません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"解説","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code><strong>handler.preventExtensions()</strong></code> メソッドは <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/preventExtensions\"><code>Object.preventExtensions()</code></a> に対するトラップです。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"interceptions","title":"介入","isH3":true,"content":"<p>このトラップは下記の操作に介入できます。</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/preventExtensions\"><code>Object.preventExtensions()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Reflect/preventExtensions\"><code>Reflect.preventExtensions()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"invariants","title":"不変条件","isH3":true,"content":"<p>以下の不変条件に違反している場合、プロキシは <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypeError\"><code>TypeError</code></a> を発生します。</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>Object.preventExtensions(<var>proxy</var>)</code> は、 <code>Object.isExtensible(<var>proxy</var>)</code> が <code>false</code> の場合のみ <code>true</code> を返します。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"preventextensions_のトラップ","title":"preventExtensions のトラップ","isH3":true,"content":"<p>次のコードでは <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/preventExtensions\"><code>Object.preventExtensions()</code></a> をトラップします。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> p <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Proxy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">preventExtensions</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">target</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'called'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">preventExtensions</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">preventExtensions</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>p<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"called\"</span>\n                                          <span class=\"token comment\">// false</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>The following code violates the invariant.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js example-bad notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> p <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Proxy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">preventExtensions</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">target</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">preventExtensions</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>p<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// TypeError is thrown</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-proxy-object-internal-methods-and-internal-slots-preventextensions\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"ja\">[[PreventExtensions]] の定義</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Proxy.handler.preventExtensions","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/preventExtensions/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect4\">\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy\"><code>Proxy</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy\"><code>handler</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/preventExtensions\"><code>Object.preventExtensions()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Reflect/preventExtensions\"><code>Reflect.preventExtensions()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"解説","id":"description"},{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"handler.preventExtensions() は Object.preventExtensions() に対するトラップです。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"handler.preventExtensions()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"handler.preventExtensions()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"handler.preventExtensions()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/proxy/proxy/preventextensions","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/proxy/proxy/preventextensions/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"JavaScript リファレンス"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Obj